  <chapter xml:id="chapter_intro">
    
    <title>Introduction to TERESAH</title>
    <para>Welcome to TERESAH. TERESAH (standing for <emphasis>Tools E-Registry for E-Social science, Arts and Humanities</emphasis>) is a web based application for the collection and organisation of data research tools. It was created using funds from the Seventh Framework Programme. </para>
    
